title: Nosferatu: The Wrath of Malachi playthrough -- Part 2
description: Well, I ended up running out of time, and I thought that I'd have to replay the game again, but I just reloaded an earlier save and skipped saving my Dad which allowed me to win. Sorry Dad, but it had to be done. Overall, cool ass game, way better than I thought it'd be.
